---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Roadmap | Wolvec"
  description="Where Wolvec is going — a directional view of what we're building toward, updated as we learn from coaches in early access."
>
  <main class="pt-32 pb-24 px-6 min-h-screen">
    <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-6">Where Wolvec is going</h1>
      <p class="text-neutral-400 text-lg mb-16 leading-relaxed">
        We ship in public and we plan in public. Here's what we're building toward.
      </p>

      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Phase 1 — Where we are now</h2>
        <p class="text-neutral-400 leading-relaxed">
          A working AI coaching layer for online fitness coaches. The 30-minute intake interview
          builds your AI without an existing content library. Per-category autonomy controls let
          you decide how much each category of interaction your AI handles, with recommended
          defaults and plain-language liability notes at every setting. PAR-Q+ pre-participation
          health screening, a coach acknowledgment gate on new client onboarding, and hard safety
          escalation rules for any mention of pain, injury, illness, or dizziness. We are
          currently onboarding design-partner coaches.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Phase 2 — Depth</h2>
        <p class="text-neutral-400 leading-relaxed">
          AI that gets better the longer it works with you. Methodology refinement: your AI learns
          your voice and approach over time from real coach-client interactions. Specialty depth
          within fitness — strength, hypertrophy, endurance, rehab. Per-client autonomy controls
          so you can set different autonomy levels for individual clients, not just per category.
          A public changelog of every change we ship.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Phase 3 — Reach</h2>
        <p class="text-neutral-400 leading-relaxed">
          A client marketplace where AI-assisted intake matches clients to verified coaches with
          live AI assistants. Quality benchmarking before any coach can take marketplace clients.
          Built on the trust we earn during Phase 1 and 2.
        </p>
      </section>

      <div class="border border-white/10 bg-brand-muted rounded-xl p-6 mb-8">
        <p class="text-neutral-400 leading-relaxed">
          We do not commit to dates. Phase 1 to Phase 2 to Phase 3 is the direction. Pace
          depends on what we learn from coaches in early access. If you are a fitness coach who
          wants to shape this, apply for early access.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-6">
          <a
            href="/#early-access"
            class="inline-block bg-brand-accent hover:bg-brand-accent/90 text-white font-semibold px-6 py-3 rounded-md transition-colors"
          >
            Apply for early access &rarr;
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
